<p>Angela joined Companies House in May 2012 as Head of Human Resources and Estates. She took up the role of Director of People Transformation in February 2018.</p>

<p>Angela has over 25 yearsâ€™ experience within the HR profession working in the NHS, police service and higher education sector.</p>

<p>Before joining Companies House Angela was Assistant Director of HR in Office for National Statistics.</p>

